## Testing Best Practices

### 1. Always Clean Up
```typescript
afterEach(async () => {
  if (createdEntityId) {
    await deleteMyEntity({
      expectToFail: false,
      input: { id: createdEntityId },
    });
  }
});
```

### 2. Use Type-Safe Inputs
```typescript
const input = {
  name: 'myEntity',
  label: 'My Entity',
} as const satisfies CreateMyEntityInput;
```

### 3. Test Edge Cases
- Empty strings
- Maximum length strings
- Special characters
- Unicode characters
- Newlines and formatting
- Null vs undefined

### 4. Snapshot Failing Tests
```typescript
expectOneNotInternalServerErrorSnapshot({
  errors,
});
```

### 5. Setup Global Test Context
